name: 39th Asia Pacific Dental and Oral Health Congress
content: 39th Asia Pacific Dental and Oral Health Congress" is organized by Conference Series LLC LTD which focuses on "Trends and Innovations in Dental and Oral Health" which will be held from March 23-24, 2020 at Yokohama, Japan. This conference is being organized in collaboration with the European Dental Society. It joins the remarkable and overall mix of dental specialist, analysts, and pioneers both from the academic network and industry over the globe to exchange their knowledge, insight, and research to make a world-class Dental and Oral Health Conference.
